        <item>
            <title>1.4.3</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 10:59:09 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>70</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## What’s fixed

- Glass notes on macOS 15 and earlier now use the system’s appearance-adaptive blur, so Light Mode no longer receives a forced dark overlay.
- Checkbox selections now treat the checkbox marker and its spacer as one control. Deleting a partial keyboard or mouse selection can no longer leave the checkbox misaligned.
]]></description>
