            <title>1.4.2</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 17:39:01 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>69</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## What’s fixed

- The menu bar now keeps showing **Update available** after you choose **Later** in the update dialog.
- Manual and automatic update checks now share the same update state, so the available-version badge remains accurate until the update is installed or is no longer newer.

This release keeps the existing adaptive blue version badge styling in both Light and Dark Mode.
]]></description>
