            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# CueNow 1.4.1

## Fixes

- Fixed numbered lists not scrolling to reveal the new current item when Return
  is pressed at the bottom of the visible note area.
- Nested numbered lists now also keep the newly inserted sub-list item fully
  visible before you begin typing.
]]></description>
